Welcome to PIXELFOODIE, an intelligent and interactive food recipe platform designed to bring authentic culinary experiences right to your screen! 

✨ Key Features
🔐 Secure Authentication: Seamless Google and Facebook login integration powered by Firebase Authentication.
🧠 PixelMood AI: An integrated custom Machine Learning model that analyzes text to suggest the perfect recipe based on your current mood! 
📱 Beautiful UI: A clean, responsive, and user-friendly interface built for food lovers.

🛠️ Tech Stack
Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript
Backend: Firebase (Authentication)
Security: Firebase (Authentication)
AI/ML Integration: Python (Text-based ML model deployment)

🚀 How to Run Locally
1. Clone this repository to your local machine.
2. Open the project folder in your favorite code editor (e.g., VS Code).
3. Since Firebase Auth is securely configured for local testing, start a local server (like the 'Live Server' extension) to run the `index.html` file on `http://127.0.0.1:5500`.
4. Log in using your Google or Facebook account and explore the recipes!

